/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n食少兩餐就得啦"},{"pid":"76cde908f555b32d87d5d891f96977009f92957b","tid":453842,"uid":39683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T03:31:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>做胸唔做背會變圓背，成個阿伯咁，毒上加毒<br />\n仲要冇諗過做腳，做完gym都冇大力過，成世比mk仔蝦</blockquote><br />\n學到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我每樣都練少少就夠<br />\n<br />\n其實我本身瘦底應該可以以淨係練結實，唔會變大？？</blockquote><br />\n唔洗驚變大，你呢個心態練極都可以保持骨感美，年紀大啲就有個肚腩仔，成個外星人咁，港仔宿命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79170d7a743022af72ea0f08006df2005f6555bf","tid":453842,"uid":37942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T03:54:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>做胸唔做背會變圓背，成個阿伯咁，毒上加毒<br />\n仲要冇諗過做腳，做完gym都冇大力過，成世比mk仔蝦</blockquote><br />\n學到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我每樣都練少少就夠<br />\n<br />\n其實我本身瘦底應該可以以淨係練結實，唔會變大？？</blockquote><br />\n唔洗驚變大，你呢個心態練極都可以保持骨感美，年紀大啲就有個肚腩仔，成個外星人咁，港仔宿命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都六舊腹肌喎其實，不過心口冇肉"},{"pid":"9300333eb592ef417f3cb059756bdab8f3353bfc","tid":453842,"uid":37942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T03:55:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>跑步黎講最好一星期唔過兩次，每次唔過30分鐘，唔係事倍功半。<br />\n另外樓主做gym基本上如果係瘦底基本上一星期去做三次，就算chur盡，做足一年都唔會橫同厚好多，講真邊有咁易。</blockquote><br />\n得。明白，"},{"pid":"4a0cf3e60535064776990e3035a38a330de2c67b","tid":453842,"uid":734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T05:16:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>做胸唔做背會變圓背，成個阿伯咁，毒上加毒<br />\n仲要冇諗過做腳，做完gym都冇大力過，成世比mk仔蝦</blockquote><br />\n學到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我每樣都練少少就夠<br />\n<br />\n其實我本身瘦底應該可以以淨係練結實，唔會變大？？</blockquote><br />\n唔洗驚變大，你呢個心態練極都可以保持骨感美，年紀大啲就有個肚腩仔，成個外星人咁，港仔宿命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都六舊腹肌喎其實，不過心口冇肉</blockquote><br />\n我睇你講d野就真係笑到有腹肌喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔想咁大隻，係呀，我揸住個啞鈴舉左兩下，第二日好似the rock咁大隻呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79b4e0effea19a6aeb673e8feecac32bcc0d00b8","tid":453842,"uid":85564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T05:22:25.000Z","msg":"你估咁易變橫咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  仲有，練胸不練背，遲早圓肩周身痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  背一定要強過胸要維持到直立正常體態，除非你想胸大但又寒背，行出街縮埋一舊咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fca003437ab1132868d318c3bd47e8aa75ac7179","tid":453842,"uid":5286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T05:26:43.000Z","msg":"屌，人哋唔想練橫咪由鳩佢囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 負評做嘜嘢 <br />\n<br />\n卧推卧拉夠㗎啦"}]}